{"tid":1630284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"詳盡分析禁蒙面法為香港帶黎嘅禍害","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:09:49.000Z","uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"891b69caf54e8b5e4d9095964535fc100254267d","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HofFBnMXkRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHofFBnMXkRs&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6lNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=662f911a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HofFBnMXkRs</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 🇭🇰時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780684890e9537a9e66b21660640b135dd4d3496","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"6e98c9cd968177802d6b8c827212f843fc7ff37d","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"反禁蒙面法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cb31968e04c4b1e1e88f4e327e8131542d43b8","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:03:36.000Z","msg":"反禁蒙面法"},{"pid":"e2bec0fbe93f99840f98ff5bcb2381f3e39013fc","tid":1630284,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:06:22.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba5a7561ad32de0be54e5389723f680a85efe98b","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"ca22557a0b6dc2882a3a99257bacccb90bf647ee","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"cb86c9827931a3aa8a57238f5f4226174f7de009","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:22:49.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"428dfcfc4dd183d0122d49cf558e03606c96e11d","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:23:08.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"88a78ed5cf110b50f9619028a3b148d7104124fc","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"3373c5ffdb3b1c39facdcfc0ab9012f2613c8256","tid":1630284,"uid":291448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply